libgweather 2.24.1
==================

libgweather

	* Make sure the returned strings are UTF-8 (Minoru Hashima, Dan)
	* Code cleanups (Dan)
	* Fix crash if a timezone in Locations.xml is not known (Dan)
	* Use the proxy settings (Dan)
